notes:
This package is [officially supported in Pyodide](https://pyodide.org/en/stable/usage/packages-in-pyodide.html).

To use it in PyScript simply add it to the `packages` section of your TOML configuration like this:

```
packages = ["executing" ]
```

Or if you're using a JSON configuration, like this:

```
{
    packages: ["executing"]
 }
```
